routeFacts.name: Schnellfahrstrecke Köln-Aachen
routeFacts.description: Köln Schnellfahrstrecke is a route featured in the base game of Train Sim World 2 which runs from Cologne to Aachen in Germany, a distance of 70 kilometres. Featured with the route is the DB BR 406 ICE 3M which operates high speed passenger services as well as the DB BR 442 which operates commuter services.
